TextBody:
Hi Team,

Thank you for contacting Netwrix technical support. Currently, Netwrix Enterprise Auditor v11.6 is compatible with the following NetApp ONTAP:

	7-Mode 7.3+
	Cluster-Mode 8.2+


The versions you mentioned (9.9 & 9.11) should have no issues with the noted exception that the Resiliency feature is not supported.

https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Requirements/Target/FileSystems.htm

Let me know if you have any other questions!

Thank you,

Tay Caliguiri

Senior Technical Support Engineer

300 Spectrum Ctr Dr #200, Irvine, CA 92618
www.netwrix.com
